<para id="RM00000137W00WX" category="G" type-id="8000T" name-id="SR05D-12" from="201202">
<name>ON-VEHICLE INSPECTION</name>
<subpara id="RM00000137W00WX_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM00000137W00WX_01_0001" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__00001T100000">
<ptxt>STEERING WHEEL FREE PLAY</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="F008463E03" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<s2>
<ptxt>Stop the vehicle. Position the steering wheel in the center position with the tires pointing straight ahead.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Turn the steering wheel gently right and left, and check the steering wheel free play.</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>Maximum free play</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>30 mm (1.18 in.)</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
<list1 type="nonmark">
<item>
<ptxt>If the free play exceeds the maximum, replace the steering intermediate shaft sub-assembly or steering link assembly.</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
